#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Beskrivning</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Resource Editor is used to create, edit, and delete resources and "
"resource groups. Resources must belong to a resource group. At the moment "
"sub-groups are not allowed."
msgstr ""
"Resurseditorn används för att skapa, redigera och ta bort resurser och "
"resursgrupper. Resurser måste höra till en resursgrupp. För närvarande "
"tillåts inte delgrupper."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Working resources must refer to a <emphasis>calendar</emphasis> that defines "
"the working hours for the resource. Calendars are created using the <link "
"linkend=\"work-and-vacation-editor\">Work and Vacation Editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Arbetande resurser måste referera till en <emphasis>kalender</emphasis> som "
"definierar resursens arbetstimmar. Kalendrar skapas genom att använda <link "
"linkend=\"work-and-vacation-editor\">Arbets- och semestereditorn</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Material resources are by default always available. You can use a calendar "
"to limit its availability."
msgstr ""
"Materiella resurser är normalt alltid tillgängliga. Du kan använda en "
"kalender för att begränsa deras tillgänglighet."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resources can be <emphasis>Shared</emphasis> or <emphasis>Local</emphasis>. "
"A local resource is only used in the current project. A shared resource can "
"be shared between multiple projects and is stored in a separate file, see "
"<link linkend=\"managing-resources\">Managing Resources</link>."
msgstr ""
"En resurs kan vara <emphasis>Delad</emphasis> eller <emphasis>Lokal</"
"emphasis>. En lokal resurs används bara i det aktuella projektet. En delad "
"resurs kan delas mellan flera projekt och lagras i en separat fil, se <link "
"linkend=\"managing-resources\">Hantera resurser</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Verktygsrad"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar provides the means to create and delete resources and resource "
"groups:"
msgstr ""
"Verktygsraden tillhandahåller möjlighet att skapa och ta bort resurser och "
"resursgrupper:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button"
msgstr "Knapp"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Genväg"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:36 resourceeditor.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Description</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Beskrivning</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Resource Group"
msgstr "Lägg till resursgrupp"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: resourceeditor.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Button to create a resource group. The new group is appended at the end of "
"the groups."
msgstr ""
"Knapp för att skapa en resursgrupp. Den nya gruppen läggs till sist i "
"grupperna."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Resource"
msgstr "Lägg till resurs"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: resourceeditor.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Button to create a resource. The new resource is appended as a child to the "
"currently selected group. If a resource is selected, the new resource is "
"appended to its parent group."
msgstr ""
"Knapp för att skapa en resurs. Den nya resursen läggs till sist som "
"underliggande till gruppen som för närvarande är markerad. Om en resurs är "
"markerad, läggs den nya resursen till i dess överliggande grupp."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Delete</para>"
msgstr "<para>Ta bort</para>"

#. Tag: keycap
#: resourceeditor.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>Delete</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>Delete</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the selected resources and/or resource groups."
msgstr "Tar bort de markerade resurserna och/eller resursgrupperna."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resources can be created by dropping data from any application that supports "
"dragging vCard information, like <emphasis>KAddressBook</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>Evolution</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Resurser kan skapas genom att släppa data från vilket program som helst som "
"stöder att dra vCard-information, såsom <emphasis>Adressboken</emphasis> "
"eller <emphasis>Evolution</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resources can be copied or moved to a different resource group using drag-"
"and-drop."
msgstr ""
"Resurser kan kopieras eller flyttas till en annan resursgrupp genom att "
"använda dra och släpp."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "When moving a resource, the resource will lose any allocations."
msgstr "När en resurs flyttas förlorar den alla tilldelningar."

#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Redigera data"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Data can be edited inline as described <link linkend=\"using-the-views"
"\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Data kan redigeras på plats som beskrivs <link linkend=\"using-the-views"
"\">här</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resources can also be edited using the Resource Settings Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Resurser kan också redigeras genom att använda resursinställningsdialogrutan."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following columns are displayed as default:"
msgstr "Följande kolumner visas normalt:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column"
msgstr "Kolumn"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Namn"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the resource or resource group."
msgstr "Resursens eller resursgruppens namn."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scope"
msgstr "Omfattning"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A resource can be <emphasis>Shared</emphasis> or <emphasis>Local</emphasis>. "
"A shared resource cannot be edited."
msgstr ""
"En resurs kan vara <emphasis>Delad</emphasis> eller <emphasis>Lokal</"
"emphasis>. En delad resurs kan inte redigeras."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Typ"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The type of resource or resource group."
msgstr "Resursen eller resursgruppens typ."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Initials"
msgstr "Initialer"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "The initials of the resource."
msgstr "Resursens initialer."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email"
msgstr "E-post"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The e-mail address of the resource."
msgstr "Resursens e-postadress."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Kalender"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "The calendar defines when the resource is working."
msgstr "Kalendern definierar när resursen arbetar."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit (%)"
msgstr "Begränsning (%)"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum load that can be assigned."
msgstr "Maximal belastning som kan tilldelas."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available From"
msgstr "Tillgänglig från"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:161 resourceeditor.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defines when the resource is available to the project."
msgstr "Definiera när resursen är tillgänglig i projektet."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Until"
msgstr "Tillgänglig till"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Rate"
msgstr "Normal taxa"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "The cost per hour, normal hours."
msgstr "Kostnad per timme, normaltid."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Konto"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "The account where the resource cost is accumulated."
msgstr "Kontot där resurskostnaden samlas."

#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Inställning"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the context menu, the view can be configured to split/unsplit the tree "
"view or it can be configured using the configure dialog."
msgstr ""
"Genom att använda den sammanhangsberoende menyn. kan vyn ställas in att dela "
"eller dra ihop trädvyn, eller anpassas med inställningsdialogrutan."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configure dialog enables you to tailor the amount of information the "
"view displays to fit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Inställningsdialogrutan låter dig skräddarsy hur mycket information vyn "
"visar, för att passa dina behov."

#~ msgid "Description"
#~ msgstr "Beskrivning"
